00:47:39.630 --> 00:47:44.490
An actor, Douglas Fairbanks
senior, was asked by a family

00:47:44.490 --> 00:47:45.570
member, how are you feeling?

00:47:45.570 --> 00:47:47.240
He said, never felt better.

