00:48:19.530 --> 00:48:20.720
there anything you
want us to know

00:48:20.720 --> 00:48:22.430
about running the business?

00:48:22.430 --> 00:48:24.780
And he said, yes, leave the
shower curtain on the inside

00:48:24.780 --> 00:48:26.940
